Purpose:

This folder contains all UI-related classes, such as Activity, Fragments, Adapters and ViewHolders files.
This is where the presentation layer resides. Each screen or UI component in the app should have
its associated activity or fragment here, along with any custom views.

What to include:

* Activity and Fragment classes
* Custom views
* Layout-related classes

Examples:

* MainActivity.kt
* LoginFragment.kt
* CustomButton.kt